name: Girl Power Adventure Scrolling Platformer!
description:
Do you have what it takes to get the girl through all 10 levels? Avoid the obstacles in the way.

Sorry there's no sound and checkpoints. When you complete all 10 levels, you win.

Use arrow keys to move the girl, good luck.

Warning: The character might not move when you first start the game, if that happens, just refresh the page, the game worked for me.
